<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ج ح ر:</span> جَمْعُ <span class="c2">(الْجُحْرِ جِحَرَةٌ)</span> كَعِنَبَةٍ وَ <span class="c2">(أَجْحَارٌ)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(الْجُحْرَانُ)</span> الْجُحْرُ.<span class="c5"> وَفِي الْحَدِيثِ:</span> <span class="c2">«إِذَا حَاضَتِ الْمَرْأَةُ حَرُمَ الْجُحْرَانُ»</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>